    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it sounds like you're saying the burden is on the small businesses to \"proactively invest\" just to survive. doesn't it seem a bit lopsided that the immediate financial strain lands almost entirely on the local manufacturer, while the environmental benefits are more of a vague, non-monetary goal for the federal government?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
